{"tid":1567273,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「915」勇武手足注意！","createTime":"2019-09-14T04:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T10:44:14.000Z","uid":35125,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"8e5717a745f54a35802d69e6080a24cab76c1cb8","tid":1567273,"uid":35125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:04:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">慎防圍捕，諗定後路</span><br />\n<br />\n聽日d狗一定又玩圍捕<br />\n以下有小小建議俾大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>準備定港島住宿</strong><br />\n假如主要幹道同隧道set road 哂block + 守哂各大mtr站<br />\n<br />\n因此唔係住港島既手足<strong>一定要</strong>諗定後路<br />\n搵定信任既人同住宿 必要時係港島過夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2.撒退時分成小隊</strong><br />\n美領個日 各大媒體直播影住手足去某地方變裝<br />\nd狗一定會逼人交cctv<br />\n而之後狗玩東西夾擊 灣仔同炮台山包抄<br />\n令有手足係維園 天后 炮台山 等地方被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以大家記住 走既時候唔好俾人影住<br />\n同<strong>信任既人</strong>分成小隊撒離 化整為零<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n往安全方向散去 <br />\n<br />\n<strong>3.半山走佬大法</strong><br />\n好多住對面海既手足都可能唔知<br />\n其實整個港島北 由西環到天后<br />\n都有好多路上半山 <br />\n半山主要得民居 地方清靜 好多小路同暗位<br />\n所以如果大家真係東西被包既話 <br />\n往南上山都係一個option<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再等安全時機離去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後 祝大家武運昌隆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f31eb2f90101c45251214194112a9a53bfc50bd4","tid":1567273,"uid":238275,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:05:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490c9c91af9c76049bbc3189df4a783612ccb9b2","tid":1567273,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a678979328fbf58790ea67fc0f7d9af0a5e7ab23","tid":1567273,"uid":35125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:05:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b99261aa17cc554ed358e4c1e673dc15bfb63b","tid":1567273,"uid":135067,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:06:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />915 12點英領 2點半銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac